description: [``botocore``] This release adds new API to reset connector metadata cache
[``botocore``] Updated ResourceType enum with new resource types onboarded by AWS Config in May 2023.
[``botocore``] Adds support for targeting Dedicated Host allocations by assetIds in AWS Outposts
[``botocore``] This release adds RecursiveInvocationException to the Invoke API and InvokeWithResponseStream API.

[``botocore``] Added support for custom domain names for Redshift Provisioned clusters. This feature enables customers to create a custom domain name and use ACM to generate fully secure connections to it.
